151
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:07,890
Morning, everyone.

152
00:07:10,460 --> 00:07:11,630
You knew to come here.

153
00:07:11,630 --> 00:07:13,480
I was going to send Jian Shu to find you.

154
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,740
How are things going with you these days?

155
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,240
Don’t mention it.

156
00:07:21,360 --> 00:07:22,760
Xue Yuan, that old prick,

157
00:07:23,090 --> 00:07:24,220
