190
00:08:35,820 --> 00:08:38,549
I’m afraid the Xue family's case will be delayed.

191
00:08:38,830 --> 00:08:40,610
That’s why I am asking you to buy time.

192
00:08:40,610 --> 00:08:41,360
As for the rest,

193
00:08:41,360 --> 00:08:43,020
I've got my own arrangements.

194
00:08:43,760 --> 00:08:45,440
I've used

195
00:08:45,470 --> 00:08:46,510
all the tricks in my book.

196
00:08:46,510 --> 00:08:47,390
I really don't know

197
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:49,200
