216
00:09:21,150 --> 00:09:23,070
It's a real blossoming of the iron tree.

217
00:09:23,070 --> 00:09:23,790
Dao Qin.

218
00:09:23,900 --> 00:09:25,000
Who's the girl

219
00:09:25,210 --> 00:09:26,770
who was willing to marry him?

220
00:09:26,770 --> 00:09:27,590
Dao Qin,

221
00:09:27,750 --> 00:09:28,810
does Ning'er know?

222
00:09:29,900 --> 00:09:31,370
She's someone under Miss Jiang?

223
00:09:31,370 --> 00:09:32,970
When I went over to the Lyu's,

224
00:09:33,320 --> 00:09:35,250
